snippet.title: Pixxelverse Online (Dev Update July 2022 - Teaser)
snippet.description:
This is our developer update for July 2022. We made a lot of changes to our UI and have started work on the world building aspect as well as adding all the features necessary for a SP to function. We are incredibly proud of our team and what we have accomplished together so far, we have a long way to go but hope this gives you a little something to look forward too.

Come join our Community Discord!
https://discord.gg/H7udUjdytk
